Package models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Album
    The album class keeps track of the photos that are added to it, the album thumbnail, and the range of the dates that the album covers
    AlbumListViewCell<T extends java.util.ArrayList<Album>>
    This class handles each cell in an a list of albums
    Photo
    The photo class keeps track of the caption that is associated with each photo, the date of the photo, the tags associated with each photo, the location of the photo, and the album it is associated with.
    PhotoListViewCell<T extends java.util.ArrayList<Photo>>
    This class manages each individual photo cell item that is displayed in the album view.
    SerialUtils
    A class used to manage serializing/storing all of the users' data.
    User
    The user class keeps track of the albums associated with this user and does bookkeeping for those albums.
